r />\n<br />\n以前佢唱歌唱得好輕鬆 宜家佢唱歌就上氣唔接下氣 求奇套左個字出黎hea住唱就算<br />\n<br />\n慘得過佢D歌迷又受</blockquote><br />\n其實佢呢個唱腔係好傷聲帶 會殘都好正常</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n認同<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n人地係用丹田嚟飆高音 佢就係用喉嚨嚟飆<br />\n不過佢由02開始飆 飆到08之後先開始壞聲都算係咁<br />\nBTW如果家下要求佢喺演唱會度一氣呵成用真音飆哂成首最長的電影唔知佢會點死法<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"084c3bb572e30b7c0266b3156250613f977f55df","tid":304251,"uid":120980,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-01T02:48:35.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>老啦佢<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n聽佢d歌個陣重點晨早都已經唔係擺係唱功<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n利申 周董死忠<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n我知<br />\n擺喺經典度吖嘛 我又何嘗唔係<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/biggrin.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e9b0fce7e0c07c02ed164d6a26847e82a9923d96","tid":304251,"uid":120980,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-01T02:50:50.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>講真 寧願佢唱得差都唔想佢搵2件垃圾乜撚野彈頭係側邊唱<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n橫掂都係難聽不如聽難聽既周杰倫<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n通常佢有意想捧紅嘅人都係捧唔紅<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"70c2a2d0fcd6d221740fc5c25429b030f01767d5","tid":304251,"uid":120980,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-01T02:54:53.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>我諗佢啲歌迷都唔會好介意佢唱功<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n應該話好少聽周董嘅人重點係放喺佢